title: Total Currency Outside the Treasury and Federal Reserve Banks for United States
notes:
Series Is Presented Here As Two Variables--(1)--Original Data, 1878-1914 (2)--Original Data, 1914-1949. Data Include Minor Coin. Beginning December 17, 192, The Circulation Statement Is Dated For End Of Month Instead Of Beginning Of The Month. Data Are Based On Revised Daily Figures. Source: U.S. Treasury Department, Computed By NBER From Data Found In Annual Report Of The Treasurer, 1886; And Circulation Statement Of U.S. Money Since 1887.

This NBER data series m14135b appears on the NBER website in Chapter 14 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter14.html.

NBER Indicator: m14135b
